This article showcases news, blog posts, and updates that VRChat published between January 1, 2018 and December 31, 2018.
==History==

Since 2016, VRChat's developer updates have been posted on several outlets, and have also gone through different names. Former developer updates have been called ''Developer Blogs'', ''Community Updates'', and ''Town Hall Meetings''.

''See [[Special:MyLanguage/2018 in VRChat updates|2018 in VRChat updates]] for all detailed information.''
